{"tid":1561904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢幾個月已經顛覆左暴力呢個詞語","createTime":"2019-09-11T19:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T19:45:08.000Z","uid":25767,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a43a86d7e9ea4305b317d2a905736a5a3ca0e2","tid":1561904,"uid":25767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:15:53.000Z","msg":"由細到大，屋企人或者老師都會教暴力係唔岩 我亦覺得有咩都要以理服人，動口不動手。但今次逃犯條例由開始百幾萬人出黎遊行 示威 表達民意 到二百萬人，成個政府視若無睹 堅持推行 到最後有示威者暴力衝擊立法會 政府先終於叫暫緩。<br />\n<br />\n係咪即係特區政府教識我地暴力係解決問題既最好方法？ 和平理性表達你都唔聽！咁點傾？唯有靠暴力表達？官逼民反？要有幾暴力先肯再聽民意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暴力係呢個時代好似已經唔係負面既意思咁"},{"pid":"9d9827551dbb2649850d67a7bcfeb81ae0665921","tid":1561904,"uid":76702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:16:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d95c542f94c03a311ba53d44e554b9892b04fbd1","tid":1561904,"uid":212640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:16:22.000Z","msg":"深水埗手足！今晚見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1561884\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1561884</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cf7408875d108139b9385c34e103699959238357","tid":1561904,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:16:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pi